With a targeted focus on nightlife and entertainment search, SloshSpot is uniquely positioned to be the site where you come when you're done working and you're ready to play. With built-in social networking features such as event planning and notification, comments and ratings, photo and video sharing, and easy integration with mobile devices, email, calendars, and existing social networks (Such as Facebook...), SloshSpot will become both an essential entertainment and event resource as well as your new online nightlife and entertainment community.

Full Description: June20 launched Converge™ in 2017, a technology platform that is changing in-store shopping by adding an interactive digital component that retailers and brands can use to explain complex products, configure design options, discover and compare similar products in a category, or display a range of similar products without sacrificing shelf space. When customers research products at home with internet searches, they must open a browser, type in the right keywords to find the information they are looking for, and then be willing to go down the “rabbit hole” of the internet. Rather than disrupting the natural shopping experience, Converge™ merges the richness of online with in-store. When a customer moves the tablet in front of a product on display, the consumer automatically gets all of the rich content that could be found online, but with no typing, no searching, no back and forth between multiple products. The experience is designed to integrate seamlessly with the way people naturally like to shop and discover items in-store.
Founders: marc meyer, Marc Meyer, Paul Chapuis
